# Tool Descriptions for Agent

## check_my_balance
Check agent's current wallet balance in SOL

## send_crypto
Request payment from the user

Args:
    recipient_name: Name of the recipient
    recipient_address: Wallet address
    amount_sol: Amount to send
    reason: Reason for the payment

## create_payment_payload
Create a payment payload for the user to sign

Args:
    recipient_name: Name of the recipient
    recipient_address: Wallet address
    amount_sol: Amount to send
    reason: Reason for the payment

## check_pardon_status
Check current status of pardon application

Returns: Status details with obstacles and strategies

